sql:
SELECT a.name
FROM Author a
JOIN Author_list al ON a.author_id = al.author_id
WHERE a.name <> 'Mckeown , Kathleen'
AND al.paper_id IN (
    SELECT al2.paper_id
    FROM Author_list al2
    JOIN Author au2 ON al2.author_id = au2.author_id
    WHERE au2.name = 'Mckeown , Kathleen'
)
GROUP BY a.author_id, a.name
ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT al.paper_id) DESC
LIMIT 1;
question: What is the name of the author who has co-authored the most papers with Mckeown , Kathleen ?

sql:
SELECT A.name
FROM Author_list AL1
JOIN Author_list AL2 ON AL1.paper_id = AL2.paper_id AND AL1.author_id != AL2.author_id
JOIN Author A ON AL2.author_id = A.author_id
WHERE AL1.author_id = (SELECT author_id FROM Author WHERE name = 'Mckeown , Kathleen')
GROUP BY A.author_id, A.name
ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
LIMIT 1;
question: What is the name of the author who has co-authored the most papers with Mckeown , Kathleen ?

sql:
SELECT a.name
FROM Author a
JOIN Author_list al ON a.author_id = al.author_id
WHERE al.paper_id IN (
    SELECT paper_id
    FROM Author_list
    WHERE author_id = (
        SELECT author_id
        FROM Author
        WHERE name = 'Mckeown , Kathleen'
    )
)
AND a.author_id <> (
    SELECT author_id
    FROM Author
    WHERE name = 'Mckeown , Kathleen'
)
GROUP BY a.author_id, a.name
ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT al.paper_id) DESC
LIMIT 1;

sql:
SELECT a.name
FROM Author a
JOIN Author_list al ON a.author_id = al.author_id
JOIN Author_list al_m ON al.paper_id = al_m.paper_id
JOIN Author am ON al_m.author_id = am.author_id
WHERE am.name = 'Mckeown , Kathleen' AND a.author_id <> am.author_id
GROUP BY a.author_id, a.name
ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT al.paper_id) DESC
LIMIT 1;

sql:

FROM Author a
JOIN Author_list al ON a.author_id = al.author_id
JOIN Author_list al2 ON al.paper_id = al2.paper_id AND al.author_id <> al2.author_id
JOIN Author a2 ON al2.author_id = a2.author_id
WHERE a2.name = 'Mckeown , Kathleen'

ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT al.paper_id) DESC
